color wheel is inferior to the old one. The old color will allow you to get 
any color in the spectrum and hue.  With the old color wheel you coul...Full ReviewI love this app for making MEMES NOT as photo editor. They added a "Thought 
Bubble and a Talk Bubble" that was the only thing missing. However, the new 
color wheel is inferior to the old one. The old color will allow you to get 
any color in the spectrum and hue.  With the old color wheel you could 
match any color quickly.  Really hope they roll back the color wheel. Love 
the new fonts updates and Gif maker. Been using it for over 2yrs now. Thx 
Don Duncan.
